node.text: Last week, we launched our exclusive On Point Collection at the VS Studio in sunny Los Angeles. Follow along for a recap of the day, from invigorating workout classes with Energy Healer @maryamajayi, Pilates Instructor @lianalevi, and Founder of @thesculptsociety @meganroup, as well as an outdoor block party, and of course, the debut of our Live Flow Sweat styles. #VSLiveFlowSweat

node.title: Event Recap: Los Angeles VS Studio Launch

node.text: @CandiceHuffine shows off two simple methods to find a flawless fit for our gorgeous Bombshell Teddy. This one-piece wonder features our Bombshell bra for ultimate lift, flirty cutouts, and delicate lace to create a stunning silhouette that checks every box.

node.title: Find Your Perfect Fit with @CandiceHuffine: The Bombshell Teddy

node.text: August 26th is Women’s Equality Day, which honors the passage of the 19th Amendment in 1920—giving women the right to vote. Over the past hundred years, many incredible women have paved the way for future generations. As a brand that celebrates and advocates for women every day, we’re asking you to join us in thanking the women in our lives—including our more than 20,000 associates—who remind us there’s nothing we can’t do. #WomensEqualityDay
